iniparser (4.1-5) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Salvatore Bonaccorso ]
  * Rename and update salsa-ci.yml based on Salsa CI Team's template
  * Bump Debhelper compat level to 13
  * Declare compliance with Debian policy 4.6.0
  * Fix buffer overflow from sprintf (Closes: #985097)
  * Fail testrun on test failure (Closes: #985099)
  * Update copyright years for debian/* packaging files
  * Updated test for when long int is not 8 byte
  * Don't send a const ptr to asprintf()
  * test/testiniparser.c: fix missing comma in token test list

  [ Debian Janitor ]
  * Replace use of deprecated $ADTTMP with $AUTOPKGTEST_TMP.
  * Set upstream metadata fields: Bug-Submit, Repository.
  * Update pattern for GitHub archive URLs from /<org>/<repo>/tags
    page/<org>/<repo>/archive/<tag> -> /<org>/<repo>/archive/refs/tags/<tag>.
  * Remove obsolete fields Contact, Name from debian/upstream/metadata
    (already present in machine-readable debian/copyright).

 -- Salvatore Bonaccorso <carnil@debian.org>  Sun, 05 Dec 2021 10:06:09 +0100

